- Controller Interface abstraction structure.
    Single interface to controller. Event driven that support subscribing a callback to a specified notification type. Handles initializing the device and storing device specific device information, like firmware, calibration, etc.

    Data Structures:
        firmware
        calibration
        power

    Procedures:
        initialize() - connects, sends init commands, populates internal structures with data.
        send_command(command_type, subcommand_type, data) - build and sends the command with specified data for manual access.
        send_rumble() - builds and sends command for rumble requests.
        subscribe_callback(callback, notif_type) - allows user to add procedures to be ran upon receiving a given notificiation

